org.universAAL.ri.gateway

Class Exporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.ri.gateway.Exporter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBusMemberRegistryListener

    public class Exporter
extends Object
implements IBusMemberRegistryListener
    Tracks BusMember through the IBusMemberRegistry, when a new BusMember is registered it is checked if it should be exported, through the exporting operation chain, and if it should then it sends all active sessions an import request.
    When a new session is created, it has to be notified to the exporter to send the new session all the issued import requests.
    There should only be one Exporter per ASG.
    Author:
    amedrano

      • stopedSession

        public void stopedSession(Session session)
        To be called when a Session is about to be closed, or is disconnected. Checks all the exported proxies and removes all references, stops them if required.
        Does not send remove-requests to peers, Importer in peers will be reseted as soon as the connection is lost.
        Parameters:
        session -
